Popular Nollywood actress, Toyin Abraham has found love again. After her broken marriage with actor Adeniyi Johnson the “The Ghost and The Tout” star has announced the great news of her engagement on social media.  According to multiple reports online the actress reportedly said yes to her man last night in front of her family and friends. Her fiancée is not one that likes to be publicized but he is a senior lawyer.  A reliable source revealed that the actress’s husband-to-be popped the golden question with a ring worth millions of Naira. Congratulations to Toyin Abraham.

			
